<A>__{shot day several huge boulders are dislodged, and the three astronauts run. wildly to escape the falling rocks. when the avalanche ends, they sprawl on the lifeless sands, breathing heavily and drenched with sweat, surrounded by enormous boulders. taylor looks about him.}
