<C>__{dodge}
<D>__{it doesn't add up. there's a mantle of dust around this planet and yet it's as humid as a jungle. thunder and lightning and yet no rain. cloud cover every night and that strange luminosity, and yet no moon.}
<A>__{landon also looks up at the sky.}
<C>__{landon}
<D>__{if only we could get a fix.}
<C>__{taylor}
<P>__{(needling him)}
<D>__{what would you learn? i've told you where you are and when you are.}
<C>__{dodge}
<P>__{(gently)}
