<C>__{taylor}
<P>__{(harshly, to landon)}
<D>__{you're more than three hundred light years from your precious planet. your loved ones have been dead and forgotten for twenty centuries. even if you could get back, they'd think you were something that fell out of a tree.}
<C>__{landon}
<P>__{(wearily)}
<D>__{all right }
