<D>__{there's only one reality left. we're here and it's now. you get ahold of that and hang on tight, or you might as well be dead.}
<C>__{landon}
<P>__{(quietly)}
<D>__{i'm prepared to die.}
<A>__{taylor turns to dodge, throws up his hands.}
<C>__{taylor}
<D>__{he's prepared to die! doesn't that make you misty? chalk up another victory for the human spirit!}
<A>__{dodge rises and moves off, o.s., either embarrassed by this colloquy or unwilling to hear it again. taylor, cigar clamped between his teeth, spins toward landon.}
